provider regression) caused a burst of cheap-tier failures and the
adaptive logic is now suppressing cheap tier even though the underlying
issue is fixed. Distinct from --no-adaptive-min-tier on execute-loop:
that flag bypasses gating for a single run; this command clears the
state so the gate makes a fresh decision.

